00:41:51,742 --> 00:41:53,903
Ginger.

734
00:41:54,912 --> 00:41:56,641
Hola, Mike.

735
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:59,148
Gusto en tenerte
de regreso, Lancelot.

736
00:41:59,183 --> 00:42:00,707
