767
00:43:57,601 --> 00:43:59,193
Por favor, no te enojes.

768
00:43:59,236 --> 00:44:01,033
Para nada.

769
00:44:02,172 --> 00:44:04,333
Hagamos algo pronto, ¿sí?

770
00:44:04,375 --> 00:44:06,343
De acuerdo.

771
00:44:09,313 --> 00:44:11,713
Alégrate, corazón.

772
00:44:11,749 --> 00:44:13,478
Me gustas.

773
00:44:13,517 --> 00:44:15,542
Gracias.

