779
00:44:39,943 --> 00:44:41,205
- Sr. Pentola.
- Dr. Pentola.

780
00:44:41,245 --> 00:44:42,769
Ah, doctor.

781
00:44:42,813 --> 00:44:45,748
Un gusto, Sr. Clayton.
Mi más sentido pésame.

782
00:44:45,783 --> 00:44:46,875
Gracias.

